<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">We Already Have a Wealth Tax. It’s Just Paid to Hedge Fund Managers.</h1>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="row featured-media-block"><figure class="featured-media" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject">
<noscript><img width="1200" height="787" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2019_1031-nyse-1200x787.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="The hand of a statue of George Washington is seen in front of the New York Stock Exchange on October 11, 2019, at Wall Street in New York City." itemprop="url" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2019_1031-nyse-1200x787.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2019_1031-nyse-200x131.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2019_1031-nyse-400x262.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2019_1031-nyse-800x525.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2019_1031-nyse-2400x1574.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"></noscript><img width="1200" height="787" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%203%202'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="The hand of a statue of George Washington is seen in front of the New York Stock Exchange on October 11, 2019, at Wall Street in New York City." itemprop="url" data-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2019_1031-nyse-1200x787.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2019_1031-nyse-200x131.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2019_1031-nyse-400x262.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2019_1031-nyse-800x525.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2019_1031-nyse-2400x1574.jpg 2400w" data-src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2019_1031-nyse-1200x787.jpg" loading="lazy">
