<article class="row hentry post-264230 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-news-analysis tag-bank-bailouts tag-bernie-sanders tag-elizabeth-warren tag-hedge-funds tag-wall-street tag-wealth-tax section-economy-and-labor primary_topic-economy" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/OpinionNewsArticle">
