<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/lets-establish-a-wealth-tax-and-give-every-family-25000-a-year/">Let’s Establish a Wealth Tax &#8212; and Give Every Family $25,000 a Year</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">An annual $25,000 income to every family would create a hugely dynamic and inclusive economy.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/john-r-talbott/" itemprop="url" rel="author">John R. Talbott</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://truthout.org' itemprop='url'>Truthout</a></span></dd>
</dl>
